00:49:18,800 --> 00:49:21,678
- Put on your pants.
- What a pleasure!

719
00:49:21,760 --> 00:49:25,036
- It must be a sin.
- It couldn’t be.

720
00:49:25,120 --> 00:49:27,475
Anshel! Come on in!

721
00:49:27,560 --> 00:49:31,155
- That's enough studying!
