727
00:49:48,600 --> 00:49:50,556
- Come on, I'll teach you.
- No.

728
00:49:50,640 --> 00:49:53,393
- Don't be afraid.
- No! I don't Like swimming!

729
00:49:53,480 --> 00:49:57,553
- Take off your clothes.
