730
00:49:57,640 --> 00:50:00,393
- Are you ashamed? Embarrassed?
- I don't want to!

731
00:50:00,480 --> 00:50:02,471
- All right!
- I don't want to!

732
00:50:02,560 --> 00:50:05,870
All right, all right. If you're that scared...

733
00:50:09,440 --> 00:50:11,510
I'm not going to force you.

734
00:50:12,560 --> 00:50:14,596
- Next time.
- Sure.

735
00:50:15,480 --> 00:50:17,436
